    Class implementing a message structure for all messages sent to and received from IChannel implementations.

    Note that this implementation does not handle its own serialization and has no behaviour. It is expected that the IChannel implementation knows how to convert this message and its components to and from an appropriate wire format.

        The automatic acknowledgment key. When this is specified by the sender the channel implementation must guarantee to send an explicit MessageType.AUTO_ACK_MESSAGE message (on the same topic) in response to the message. Like all messages it is still delivered to the receiver, however, this flag instructs the channel implementation itself to return send the acknowledgment.
